    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/9b311fc11086eba7d99952c659e09921.poster.avif?t=1764149578\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/9b311fc11086eba7d99952c659e09921.webm?t=1764149578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/9b311fc11086eba7d99952c659e09921.mp4?t=1764149578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>那是1918年。您是退役的英国军医亨利·威尔斯少校，在第一次世界大战的噩梦中应召回军负责一家野战医院。这家医院人手不足，物资不足，是西线无数士兵最后的希望堡垒。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/de109b1110784f7c0ebddda526cda14f.poster.avif?t=1764149578\" width=600 height=155 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/de109b1110784f7c0ebddda526cda14f.webm?t=1764149578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>您的主要目标是保持团队士气，跟您治疗的士兵一起支持抗战。<br>为此，您需要管理好这家野战医院，负责治疗每次战斗后送入的大量受伤士兵。确保按优先级收纳病人，然后再选择治疗、安排手术还是让他们听天由命……<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/9666eb2e781a7a3e5e540d63ac11aa78.poster.avif?t=1764149578\" width=600 height=155 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/9666eb2e781a7a3e5e540d63ac11aa78.webm?t=1764149578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>尽管需求不断增长，但是资源有限……学会适应每种新情况，有时做出道德上艰难的决定。<br>决定对您的设施做出哪些改进，运用军事医学可用的最新技术。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/f03c4bc858907121beb1bba8f27ba73f.poster.avif?t=1764149578\" width=600 height=155 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1553000/extras/f03c4bc858907121beb1bba8f27ba73f.webm?t=1764149578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>一款以战争为主题的游戏，颂扬生命，而非死亡。<br></li><li>面对历史上最血腥战争之一的考验和挑战。<br></li><li>管理您的人员及其任务和疲乏。医生、护士、工程师，聘用谁由您决定。<br></li><li>您做出叙事选择。这真正影响游戏如何展开。<br></li><li>研究改进方案，以更好地满足不断变化的要求。<br></li><li>这款游戏在帝国战争博物馆的支持下开发，带来更真实的沉浸体验。</li></ul>",
